aristaIfMIB.name: aristaIfMIB
aristaIfMIB.contactinfo: Arista Networks, Inc. Postal: 5453 Great America Parkway Santa Clara, CA 95054 Tel: +1 408 547-5500 E-mail: snmp@arista.com
aristaIfMIB.description: The MIB module for reporting additional interface statistics on Arista devices.

aristaIfTable.name: aristaIfTable
aristaIfTable.description: This table contains additional interface statistics not contained in the IF-MIB.

aristaIfEntry.name: aristaIfEntry
aristaIfEntry.description: An entry containing statistics for a given interface.

aristaIfCounterLastUpdated.name: aristaIfCounterLastUpdated
aristaIfCounterLastUpdated.description: The value of sysUpTime at which the counters in the ifTable and ifXTable were sampled from the hardware.

aristaIfRateInterval.name: aristaIfRateInterval
aristaIfRateInterval.description: The amount of time over which the aristaIf*Rate values are averaged for this interface.

aristaIfInPktRate.name: aristaIfInPktRate
aristaIfInPktRate.description: The rate, in packets per second, of packets inbound on this interface, averaged over aristaIfRateInterval.

aristaIfOutPktRate.name: aristaIfOutPktRate
aristaIfOutPktRate.description: The rate, in packets per second, of packets outbound on this interface, averaged over aristaIfRateInterval.

aristaIfInOctetRate.name: aristaIfInOctetRate
aristaIfInOctetRate.description: The rate, in octets per second, of data inbound on this interface, averaged over aristaIfRateInterval.

aristaIfOutOctetRate.name: aristaIfOutOctetRate
aristaIfOutOctetRate.description: The rate, in octets per second, of data inbound on this interface, averaged over aristaIfRateInterval.

aristaIfRatesLastUpdated.name: aristaIfRatesLastUpdated
aristaIfRatesLastUpdated.description: The value of sysUpTime at which the aristaIf*Rate gauges were last calculated.

aristaIfOperStatusChanges.name: aristaIfOperStatusChanges
aristaIfOperStatusChanges.description: The number of times since system boot that ifOperStatus has changed.

aristaIfCompliance.name: aristaIfCompliance
aristaIfCompliance.description: The compliance statement for Arista devices that implement the IF-MIB

aristaIfAdditionalInformationGroup.name: aristaIfAdditionalInformationGroup
aristaIfAdditionalInformationGroup.description: A collection of objects providing additional information above and beyond what the IF-MIB provides, applicable to all network interfaces.
